poopypants mcstupidhead.

10:10.310 --> 10:12.444
Ha-ha, dookus!

10:15.115 --> 10:17.749
-What about us?
-Aren't we in it?

10:17.751 --> 10:19.718
Yeah, you sit on the side
and don't talk.

10:21.788 --> 10:23.455
That seems fair.

10:23.457 --> 10:26.992
Now, if you'll excuse me,
i have a missing actress
to locate.

10:26.994 --> 10:28.627
You gonna call in the fbi?

10:28.629 --> 10:33.898
No, i... Was just gonna
look around, but, hey!

10:35.268 --> 10:37.435
You see, maya,
i have good ideas.

10:37.437 --> 10:40.872
Worst...
Sidekick... Ever.

10:44.945 --> 10:50.582
Free time. I don't remember
the last time i had free time.
What does one do with free time?

10:56.623 --> 10:58.657
Yes?

10:58.659 --> 11:01.326
Define felony.

11:01.328 --> 11:06.598
Oh my gosh. It's
anastasia boulangerie
and she's holding a radiator.

11:06.600 --> 11:08.833
<i>Oui.</i>
I am holding a radiator
because the fbi

11:08.835 --> 11:12.003
Is hot on my trail
and they had to move me.

11:12.005 --> 11:16.174
I believe you are familiar
with my captors?

11:16.176 --> 11:17.676
Captors?

11:17.678 --> 11:20.111
No, we only borrowed
her, mommy.

11:20.113 --> 11:21.513
Did they only borrow you?

11:21.515 --> 11:23.348
Actually, i am enjoying
myself, yes.

11:23.350 --> 11:25.350
Okay, good.
Because otherwise
it's kidnapping!

11:25.352 --> 11:27.786
-Don't do that!
-We won't.

11:27.788 --> 11:29.020
There are consequences,
you know.

11:29.022 --> 11:30.055
Oh.

11:32.626 --> 11:36.895
Anastasia boulangerie
is actually bobbie jo
thibodeux, my old friend

11:36.897 --> 11:38.663
From possum trot, arkansas.

11:38.665 --> 11:42.000
Really?
That's a little hard
to believe.

11:42.002 --> 11:43.968
(hillbilly accent)
well, believe it, sister.

11:45.839 --> 11:49.074
You know, i know
it's hard to believe,
but it's true.

11:49.076 --> 11:51.076
We were best friends.

11:51.078 --> 11:54.479
I don't know about that.
Real best friends don't
fall apart.

11:54.481 --> 11:56.881
Real best friends
would do anything
for each other.

11:56.883 --> 12:00.485
But i bet that you have
loads of best friends

12:00.487 --> 12:02.420
Now that you're rich
and famous.

12:04.157 --> 12:06.825
I'm sorry, katy.

12:06.827 --> 12:10.128
I'm sorry that i made it
hard to believe.

12:14.501 --> 12:16.935
I'm katy grace.

12:18.905 --> 12:21.106
And i'm bobbie jo.

12:21.108 --> 12:23.041
And together...

12:23.043 --> 12:26.711
Both:
We are the singin'
possum trotters!

12:26.713 --> 12:28.947
♪ dingdingadingdingdinga
dingdingding ♪

12:28.949 --> 12:30.532
♪ dingadingading dingading
dingding ♪

12:30.533 --> 12:32.116
♪ oh there's a fish
and a bear and a cow
over there ♪

12:32.119 --> 12:34.452
Both:
♪ but you won't find
better friends nowhere ♪

12:34.454 --> 12:36.020
♪ 'cause i'm katy grace ♪

12:36.022 --> 12:37.756
♪ and i'm bobbie jo ♪

12:37.758 --> 12:40.358
♪ now wind us up
and watch us go! ♪

12:40.360 --> 12:45.964
-Oh boy, oh boy, oh boy.
-Mommy, mommy, mommy!

12:45.966 --> 12:48.767
Oh, i would love
to do-si-do with you,

12:48.769 --> 12:51.102
But i can't unless you unlock me
from this radiator.

12:51.104 --> 12:52.237
Do you trust me, old friend?

12:52.239 --> 12:54.706
I've always trusted you. Maya?

12:54.708 --> 12:56.808
-Are you sure, mom?
-I'm sure.

13:03.416 --> 13:05.150
(sighs)

13:07.988 --> 13:10.121
It was nice knowin' you.

13:14.728 --> 13:17.796
All right,
let's do this thing.

13:17.798 --> 13:20.665
-A woohoo!
-♪ oh, i'm bobbie jo ♪

13:20.667 --> 13:22.567
♪ and i'm katy grace ♪

13:22.569 --> 13:24.435
Both:
♪ and we go
together anyplace ♪

13:24.437 --> 13:26.571
Ah-woohoo!

13:26.573 --> 13:28.139
Ah-yeehah!

13:28.141 --> 13:29.340
♪ it's me and you
and you and me ♪

13:29.342 --> 13:31.309
♪ and that's the way
it'll always be ♪

13:31.311 --> 13:33.144
-Is it over?
-It has to be!

13:33.146 --> 13:34.245
Big finish!

13:34.247 --> 13:36.181
No, it isn't over.

13:37.450 --> 13:41.586
♪ we go together,
we're friends forever ♪

13:41.588 --> 13:43.788
♪ and ever and ever ♪

13:43.790 --> 13:46.191
-Ooh...
-What?

13:48.795 --> 13:51.329
Just real feelings.

13:53.600 --> 13:55.466
We played all the county fairs.

13:55.468 --> 14:00.371
Promised each other...
That if either one of us
ever got famous,

14:00.373 --> 14:02.674
We'd be happy for each other.

14:04.377 --> 14:05.543
I always have been.

14:05.545 --> 14:08.346
Bobbie jo, i would never
take anything away from you.

14:08.348 --> 14:12.383
I know that, katy.
I know you wouldn't.

14:12.385 --> 14:15.653
Look at you two.
Is fame and fortune
really worth

14:15.655 --> 14:17.822
