from your best friend?

14:17.824 --> 14:19.257
-Yeah.
-Of course not.

14:22.229 --> 14:23.995
I don't get this.

14:23.997 --> 14:26.297
-Neither do i.
-I don't care how famous
you got.

14:26.299 --> 14:28.299
Friends are supposed
to be friends.

14:28.301 --> 14:30.735
Why didn't
you miss her more?

14:32.072 --> 14:34.739
Well, i think maybe
she did.

14:34.741 --> 14:37.842
Yeah. The way i see it,
you could've lifted up
that radiator

14:37.844 --> 14:39.844
And gotten away
any time you wanted.

14:39.846 --> 14:42.046
